The sun reflects off Shapeir's many towers.	陽光映照在夏皮爾的無數尖塔上。
How's about a nice... Wait?!... What is-a that up there?	來喔，要不要來點...等等？！...那上面是什麼東西？
Could not find Hero file -- %s.	找不到英雄檔案──%s。
I'm terribly sorry.  That doesn't seem to be a proper Quest for Glory I character save file.	非常抱歉，這似乎不是有效的《英雄傳奇 I》角色存檔。
