Please insert the disk on which you saved your winning Hero from "Quest for Glory I: So You Want To Be A Hero" into the disk drive so that your Hero can make the journey to Shapeir.	請將您《英雄傳奇 I：你想成為英雄》(So You Want To Be A Hero) 中存下的過關英雄磁碟片，插入磁碟機，讓英雄能啟程前往夏皮爾。
